org.miller.gwt.client.sound
Class SoundOptions

java.lang.Object
  org.miller.gwt.client.sound.SoundOptions

public class SoundOptions
extends java.lang.Object

SoundOptions is a wrapper around every option you can pass into SoundManager. Each of these options are set on the SMSound object being created.
